### E1 unclosed tag (EOF)
sonar!: '<Container>' opened at offset 0 is never closed (E1)

### E1 mismatched close
sonar!: '<Container>' opened at offset 0 is closed by '</Box>' (E1)

### E2 malformed attr (no =)
sonar!: attribute 'title' is missing '=' at offset 11 (E2)

### E2 unquoted value
sonar!: attribute 'text' value must be "literal" or {expr} at offset 11 (E2)

### E3 unknown attr with suggestion
sonar!: 'Text' has no attribute 'tex' (did you mean 'text'?) (E3)

### E3 unknown attr no suggestion
sonar!: 'Text' has no attribute 'zzz' (E3)

### E4 id inside for
sonar!: 'id' is not allowed inside a $for body (E4)

### E5 unbalanced brace
sonar!: unbalanced '{' in an expression, reached end of template (E5)

### E6 for missing var
sonar!: '$for in' expected 'in' at offset 21 (E6)

### E8 empty payload
sonar!: empty template payload (E8)

### E8 text root
sonar!: template must begin with a tag, not text (E8) at offset 0

### E9 theme deferred
sonar!: 'theme' attribute is not supported in v1 — use setStyle after construction (E9)

